Aarestuhin si Cha Mu-hee.

00:35:13.361 --> 00:35:14.612
Hindi naman natin puwedeng makuha 'yan, 'di ba?

00:35:20.034 --> 00:35:24.247
Dahil wala tayong gagawing pelikula bukas,
